OL,3,CGas workers plead not guilty to 10
OL,4,Cmanslaughter charges after explosion
OL,6,FThree Jersey gas workers have pleaded
OL,7,Fnot guilty to all 10 charges of gross
OL,8,Fnegligence manslaughter after an
OL,9,Fexplosion at a block of flats in St
OL,10,FHelier.
OL,12,FTen residents died following the
OL,13,Fincident at Haut du Mont on Saturday
OL,14,F10 December 2022.
OL,16,FNeil Armstrong, 56, Lee Ward, 57, and
OL,17,FJohn Wright, 59, worked for the
OL,18,Fcompany Island Energy at the time and
OL,19,Fmade their first appearance before
OL,20,FJersey's Royal Court on Wednesday 28
OL,21,FMay 2025.
