OL,6,FThe Court also heard that at least one
OL,7,Fof the three gas workers still works
OL,8,Ffor the business.
OL,10,FSeparately, Island Energy CEO Graeme
OL,11,FMillar pleaded not guilty on behalf of
OL,12,Fthe company to two charges of breaking
OL,13,Fhealth and safety law.
OL,15,FThose alleged offences are failing in
OL,16,Ftheir duties to ensure the health and
OL,17,Fsafety of employees, and members of
OL,18,Fthe public.
OL,20,FThe trial is not expected to take
OL,21,Fplace until at least 2026.
